  type: article
  title: >-
    An Open, Transparent Macronutrient-Derived Insulinogenic Surrogate
    (NIS v1.1.6): An Exploratory Methodology Study with Out-of-Sample
    Ablation, Deterministic Feature Classification, and Post-Hoc TOST
    Equivalence Analysis
  authors:
    - given-names: Ivan
      family-names: Inkov
      email: i.inkov@nutramilo.bg
      affiliation: International Sci Ink Press Ltd EOOD, Sofia, Bulgaria
  year: 2026
